reference-text\">בהגש\"פ במקומו.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">בא יג, יד.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chabadlibrary.org/books/11200010582\">שיחת ליל ב' דחג הפסח תשכ\"ח</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413060643\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.133 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.775 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1420/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 18997/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 18883/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/100\nExpensive parser function count: 6/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4199/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.070/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6467584/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  667.250      1 -total\n 49.71%  331.700      6 תבנית:הערה\n 25.29%  168.754      2 תבנית:ניווט_קבוצות\n 25.08%  167.348      1 תבנית:פסח\n  8.90%   59.376      1 תבנית:ציטוט\n  8.36%   55.815      1 תבנית:ערך_מורחב\n  7.41%   49.446      1 תבנית:תת_קבוצה\n  6.15%   41.024      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  2.62%   17.506      1 תבנית:הפניה_לערך_מורחב/קוד\n  1.93%   12.873      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:75268-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413060643 and revision id 815095. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
